{"id": 1913, "genre": 1000, "title": "App设计中的有哪些思维定势，让你用起来觉得不顺畅？", "description": "最近你抛弃或者不爱用一个 App 了，通常是什么原因？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 18019, "comment_count": 45, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170918160956nN8XRSOoqWAvC0s5.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-19T17:00:50Z", "questions": [{"id": 3000, "title": "App设计中的有哪些思维定势，让你用起来觉得不顺畅？", "content": "你看不惯 App 设计中的哪些思维定势？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 236340, "content": "机关太多经常误操作，抖一抖手机就会弹出“问题反馈”", "image": "img/option/option/201709181659168Zs5RgdEqMA2kDWO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236345, "content": "网页版隔三差五要重新登录，首选就是用手机该APP扫码，感到麻烦", "image": "img/option/option/20170918170855rc0OugQxkbSYAUL6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236341, "content": "拒绝多次还是一直弹出更新提示，还不告知主要更新理由", "image": "img/option/option/20170918170121DdtK29OU5gp0Fywe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236343, "content": "配色单一，针对女生就是粉色，要促销就是红橙等亮色", "image": "img/option/option/201709181704491nPRxHTeJaKLDipc.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236344, "content": "用微信等社交网络登录，结果用同个平台登陆的好友们都知道了我的信息", "image": "img/option/option/20170918170555pEQ2l1SZkJD6gRvX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236342, "content": "为了推动用户注册，设置门槛，不注册就不能用", "image": "img/option/option/20170918170326v2ycafDzFxsheJVY.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236347, "content": "不断推送系统消息，用小红点让用户以为是友邻，困扰", "image": "img/option/option/20170918170941HVtI4uGWhf97wy2U.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236383, "content": "跟你说：开推送吧，你快开推送吧，开了推送我们才能更好地一起玩耍哟~", "image": "img/option/option/2017091817254381zUD7JTqhugQify.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}